<% provide(:title, "Home") %>

<body>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <div id="carousel-example-generic" class="carousel slide">
                        <!-- Indicators -->
                        <ol class="carousel-indicators hidden-xs">
                            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                        </ol>

                        <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="item active">
			                    <%= image_tag("earth.jpg", class:"img-responsive img-full") %>

                                <!-- <img class="img-responsive img-full" src="img/slide-1.jpg" alt=""> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                            	<%= image_tag("watch.jpg", class:"img-responsive img-full") %>
                                <!-- <img class="img-responsive img-full" src="img/slide-2.jpg" alt=""> -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                            	<%= image_tag("study.jpg", class:"img-responsive img-full") %>

                                <!-- <img class="img-responsive img-full" src="img/slide-3.jpg" alt=""> -->
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Controls -->
                        <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="prev">
                            <span class="icon-prev"></span>
                        </a>
                        <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="next">
                            <span class="icon-next"></span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="brand-before">
                        <small>Welcome to</small>
                    </h2>
                    <h1 class="brand-name">Earth Watch Study Group</h1>
                    <hr class="tagline-divider">
                    <h2>
                        <small>By
                            <strong>Fred Graham-Yooll</strong>
                        </small>
                    </h2>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">Discovering 
                        <strong>new answers</strong>
                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                    <!-- <img class="img-responsive img-border img-left" src="img/intro-pic.jpg" alt=""> -->
                    <hr class="visible-xs">
                    <p>The world is a n ever changing place. And as we all know, the present time faces terrific challenges that must be dealt with, or else the consequences can be, and I beleive will be, catastrophic.  Which is why I have set out to write and educate not only myself, but hopefuly others about the state of our world and the actions wee could take.</p>
                    <p>With that being said, I also beleive the studying the history could lead us in the right direction and teach us something about ourselves today.  For many deacdes, I have been fascinated with the study of ancient Egypt. In particular the reign of Cleopatra and her escapades, intelligence, and explorations throught out her world.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">
                        <strong>Cleopatras Lost Treasure</strong> by Fred Graham-Yooll
                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                    <p>I wrote a book (actually a couple) about Cleoatra and her genius-ness.</p>
                    <p>You can find it on <%= link_to("Amazon", "https://www.amazon.com/Cleopatras-Lost-Treasure-Fred-Graham-Yooll-ebook/dp/B00U0N34ZU#nav-subnav", :target => "_blank")%>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <!-- /.container -->

    

    <!-- jQuery -->
    <script src="js/jquery.js"></script>

    <!-- Bootstrap Core JavaScript -->
    <script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Script to Activate the Carousel -->
    <script>
    $('.carousel').carousel({
        interval: 5000 //changes the speed
    })
    </script>

</body>

</html>
 

